Want to go all the way with customization? No problem! With CSS overrides you can make it even look like this. The sky is the limit. Just write your overrides at the bottom of the &lsquo;style.css&rsquo; file in the &lsquo;/static/css/&rsquo; directory. Look for the following line in this files and write your CSS below:
/*------------ CSS overrides below --------------*/ Customization examples Some examples of website that use Hugobricks:
https://www.aadprins.preview.usecue.com https://www.postgrowthcities.com https://www.

Youtube is a popular video streaming service ( from a company that is known for tracking and profiling, though). The solution is to host the poster yourself and link it to Youtube. This can be done using this shortcode.
You can see it in action on the Elements page. To show a Youtube video embed, write the following &lsquo;code&rsquo;:
{{&lt; youtube &#34;qtIqKaDlqXo&#34; &#34;/uploads/youtubeposter.jpg&#34; &gt;}}
